3. cs.SOC (Computer Science and Society) - The paper discusses the importance of deliberative decision-making in democratic societies. 
4. cs.DS (Computer Science and Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper proposes a method for approximating the generalized median of participant opinions, which involves algorithmic techniques.
